public class Player
extends MovingGuest

The player which can walk around on the board, eat food, and die when meeting a monster.

meetPlayer

protected boolean meetPlayer(PlayerMove theMove)
Another player wants to occupy this player's state. With one player active this will be impossible, but with multiple players this may happen. In any case, the move itself will not be possible.

Specified by:
meetPlayer in class Guest
Parameters:
theMove - move object representing intended move and its effects.
Returns:
